des: Play an interesting game of quiz with Alexa. This skill assist you with preparing for any Social Work base exams. It is a fun way to learn and play. While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
